fields.name: Kingsley Vale
fields.description: Oil painting on stretched canvas - 83 x 74 cm - Framed in neutral grey moulding. The Yew trees of Kingsley Vale are such wonderful examples of unpruned or managed trees, allowed to follow their natural form. Painted in great detail with a highly coloured palette.
